TextChange: I don't know what else to write... I'm a faster writer than the study may have initially been designed for. I type for a living. I do tasks very quickly. I've tripled the minimum... It would be nice if I could have submitted early, as clearly I didn't take advantage of the study.
\nI know you can monitor my keystrokes. Please do not punish me or throw away my data because I performed the task quicker than expected. Please.
